column2: SELECT    o.objid, o.specobjid,o.ra,o.dec,w.z, o.petromag_u,o.petromagerr_u, o.petromag_g,o.petromagerr_g,o.petromag_r,o.petromagerr_r,   o.petromag_i,o.petromagerr_i,o.petromag_z,o.petromagerr_z,   q.Flux_OII_#,q.Flux_OII_#_err, q.Flux_Hb_#, q.Flux_Hb_#_err,q.Flux_OIII_#,Flux_OIII_#_err,   q.Flux_Ha_#,q.Flux_Ha_#_err into mydb.exclu_#_info2 FROM MyDB.MyTable AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    JOIN PhotoObjall AS o ON n.objid=o.objid   JOIN emissionlinesport as q ON o.specobjid=q.specobjid   JOIN specobjall as w ON o.specobjid=w.specobjid
